<title>ạ̉rkḍ ạ̹lyk ạ̉yhạ ạlḥbyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉rkḍ ạ̹lyk ạ̉yhạ ạlḥbyb ḥyn try̱ ʿyny shạmạaⁿ tṭyr
 ạ̉rkḍ ạ̹lyk ạ̉nt ly qryb fạ̉nt lnfsy kẓly tsyr
 (fạ̉nt ly trs wạ̉nt ly ʿz wạ̉nt slạḥy ạ̉srʿ ạ̹lyk)2

[V2]
 2- ạ̉sẖʿl ʿdwy nyrạnạaⁿ ktẖyfẗ wạ̉hạj ḥwly ryḥh ạlmkẖyfẗ
 fṣrkẖt rby kẖymty ḍʿyfẗ flạ ttrkny bnfs ạ̉syfẗ
 (fạ̉nt ạ̉lyfy mw̉nsy ạllṭyf fy ạ̉twn ạlnạr snd ạlḍʿyf)2

[V3]
 3- ạ̉nt ly fy bḥr ạlḥyạẗ ṭryqy mslk qwym fy lj ạlmyạh
 mrkbạt jysẖ ạ̉ḥạṭt bnfsy ṣrt ḥwly swrạaⁿ bạbạaⁿ llnjạẗ
 (ạ̉htf ạ̉gẖny ẓạfrạaⁿ yạ rby sḥqt ʿdwy wạ̉nrt drby)2</lyrics>
</song>